  "slug": "the-overflow-and-circulation-activation",
  "title": "The Overflow and Circulation Activation",
  "subtitle": "A weekly ritual for deepening the relationship between giving, receiving, and continuous flow",
  "excerpt": "A weekly ritual ceremony from Week 9 of the Money Journal program. Works through the five-part ceremony shape with the specific intention of releasing fear of running out and allowing effortless circulation of money and opportunity.",
  "type": "PRACTICE",
  "sourceNotes": "Adapted from Week 9 Ritual in MONEY Journal (Rebecca Page, 2025). Used with permission as part of the homemade.education Mindset library.",
  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A weekly ritual for the fear that giving freely means less arriving, and for the guilt that comes with having more than the people around you. Works through the ceremony shape: prepare, release, allow, integrate, anchor.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to rituals? Read ",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "text": "how rituals work",
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "link",
                "attrs": {
                  "href": "/mindset/how-rituals-work"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": " first.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "The practice",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Prepare",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Light a candle or hold something meaningful. Picture yourself at the centre of a current that moves both toward and away from you, money, opportunity, support, generosity, all in motion.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Release (repeat x3)",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "pullQuote",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "text": "I am ready to release all fear of running out, all guilt about having more, and all hesitation around giving freely. I release it now. I release it now. I release it now.",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Allow (repeat x3)",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "pullQuote",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "text": "I am ready to align to and allow effortless circulation of money, love, and opportunity. I allow it now. I allow it now. I allow it now.",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Integrate",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Take a slow breath in and all the way out. Imagine the current continuing to flow, money arriving and leaving without panic in either direction, each wave steady.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Anchor",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Write this anchor statement in your own handwriting. Say it aloud:",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "pullQuote",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "text": "This week, overflow and generosity move together in every area of my life.",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Where this practice comes from",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Adapted from the Week 9 Ritual in MONEY Journal (Rebecca Page, 2025). Part of the 12-week Money Journal ceremony series.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      }
